 approved by the Office of Management and Budget with the control number 3095&hyph;0016. * * * * * §1254.8 [Amended] 9. In §1254.8, paragraph (c) is amended by removing the term ``National Archives Field Archives Branch'' and adding the term ``Regional Archives.'' 10. Section 1254.10 is revised to read as follows: §1254.10 Registration. Researchers must register each day they enter a research facility, furnishing the information asked on the registration sheet and may be asked to provide additional personal identification.
